No. 1868,

Misc.

Neal et al. v. Saga Shipping Co., S. A., et al. Arthur J. Mandell for petitioners. E. D. Vickery for Saga Shipping Co., S. A., and Robert Eikel for Strachan Shipping Co., respondents.

C. A. 5th Cir. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Black and Mr. Justice Douglas are of the opinion that certiorari should be granted.
